room_title: Escape room "Area 405" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: We escaped the Area 405 Room in 35 minutes with 2 people. Wahoo!!

room_title: Escape room "Area 405" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: I booked this with a Black Friday deal for my daughter's 13th birthday. They chose Area 405. They loved it! They didn't escape in time but they didn't care. The employees said they were pretty close to solving it and they got stuck where most people get stuck. She wants to do it again!

room_title: Escape room "Area 405" by The Escape Omaha in Omaha
review: We had a room booked the day after my birthday and the staff was awesome. They gave us great customer service and it was super fun. Area 51-themed room was amazing, the clues were medium leveled but we had experienced friends and successfully broke out. Lots of fun!
